text: Natasha Pace (born 10 December 1974) is a Maltese footballer who plays as a defender for First Division club Mosta FC. She has been a member of the Malta women's national team. ==References== Category:1974 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Maltese women's footballers Category:Malta women's international footballers Category:Mosta F.C. players
